formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1	Sale value of the unsold property taken as certify by the management.									
2	Estimated construction value of the project taken as certify by the engineer.									
3	Technical measurement taken as provided by the management.									
4	Actual cost taken as per books of accounts upto 31.10.2019. 									
5	The date mentioned at column Date of agreement of sale is date of sale deed where date of agreement of sale is not available.									
6	The details mentioned at column Allotee name, Type of KYC, KYC ID and Mobile Numberis taken as certified by the management.									
7	The physical progress of the project as certified by the architect (Form-1) and engineer (Form-2) seems in coherence with actual expenditure incurred & paid considering project specifications
